<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1919-05-28T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1919-05-28T00:00:00-05:00" n="75" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d75">
                    <note rend="inline" type="source">Paris Peace Conf. 184.00101/76</note>
                    <head><hi rend="italic">Minutes of the Daily Meetings of the Commissioners
                            Plenipotentiary, Wednesday, May 28, 1919</hi></head>
                    <dateline>
                        <date ana="#date_undated-inferred-from-document-head" calendar="gregorian" when="1919-05-28">May 28, 1919</date>
                    </dateline>
                    <list type="participants">
                        <item>Present: <list>
                                <item><hi rend="smallcaps">Mr. Lansing</hi></item>
                                <item><hi rend="smallcaps">Mr. White</hi></item>
                                <item><hi rend="smallcaps">Gen. Bliss</hi></item>
                                <item><hi rend="smallcaps">Mr. Herter</hi></item>
                            </list></item>
                    </list>
                    <list>
                        <label>1.</label>
                        <item>Memorandum No. 297 was read regarding the release of Major Whitehouse
                            from duty with the Commission. The Commissioners approved of Major
                            Whitehouse’s release. <seg type="margin">Release of Major
                                Whitehouse</seg></item>
                        <label>2.</label>
                        <item>Memorandum No. 298 was read regarding the release of Major James
                            Steinberg from further duty with the Commission. The Commissioners
                            approved of Major Steinberg’s release. <seg type="margin">Release of
                                Major Steinberg</seg></item>
                    </list>
                </div>
                </body></text></TEI>